1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:56,719
I'm using the toilet.

4
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:57,280
- No.
- No.

5
00:00:58,144 --> 00:00:58,719
Why not?

6
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,880
The toilet is broken.

7
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:01,759
Use a public one.

8
00:01:01,759 --> 00:01:03,920
You broke the toilet just by using it?

9
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:05,079
Yeah, I broke it.

10
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:06,599
Come on.

11
00:01:07,968 --> 00:01:08,519
Go ahead.

12
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:11,000
You were in there so long
just to fix the toilet?

13
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,200
Let's go to a public bathroom.

14
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,719
Do you need me
to explain it to your boyfriend?

15
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:49,680
Mrs. Ji, Xuan, I should leave now.

16
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,104
See you next week.

17
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,239
Okay.

18
00:01:53,024 --> 00:01:53,879
Work is important.

19
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:54,528
I'm leaving.

20
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,879
Mr. Song, I'll go out.

21
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,519
Aren't you using the toilet?

22
00:02:05,216 --> 00:02:07,760
I changed my mind.

23
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,879
Mr. Song, I'm done. I'm going out.

24
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,439
Something's off.

25
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,819
A home-wrecker and a pick-me.

26
00:02:22,016 --> 00:02:23,479
No wonder something felt off.

27
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:24,879
Let me ask you.

28
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:28,560
If a guy were secretly
dating your girlfriend,

29
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,879
what would you do first?

30
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,240
I'd kill him.

31
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,800
But,

32
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:39,120
Wu Rui just took one look
at me and bolted.

33
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,759
You mean him and Ji Xuan...?

34
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:42,639
It's fake.

35
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,360
It must be fake.

36
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,439
But it doesn't help.

37
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:50,120
If they keep denying it,
you're still the other man.

38
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,240
What can you do?

39
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,199
I have a good idea.

40
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,960
I'm all ears.

41
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,400
Do as I've arranged.

42
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:19,439
(Wu Rui)
(Asleep?)

43
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,879
Not yet.

44
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,719
Mr. Qiu.

45
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,520
(How have you been?)

46
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,520
(You know how it is.)

47
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,919
(I understand.)

48
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,199
(Walking a tightrope every day.)

49
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,000
(Mr. Song excels in every way.)

50
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,319
(But being too excellent
can be annoying.)

51
00:04:02,688 --> 00:04:04,759
(By the way,
how are things with Miss Ji?)

52
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,240
(Pretty good.)

53
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,719
(You two are a fake couple, right?)

54
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,360
(You can fool others, but not me.)

55
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,399
(Wow.)

56
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:31,160
(You have sharp eyes.)

57
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,000
(You saw right through us.)

58
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:47,319
(Then why did you tell
Mr. Song you're her boyfriend?)

59
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:54,879
(It was originally to deal with
parents' nagging about marriage.)

60
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,600
(But Mr. Song)

61
00:04:57,984 --> 00:04:59,759
(seems to have a thing for Ji Xuan,)

62
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,720
(while she doesn't have those feelings.)

63
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,879
(I'm already her fake boyfriend,)

64
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,839
(so what's one more performance?)

65
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,279
(You must keep this secret.)

66
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:12,680
(Don't worry. I'm tight-lipped.)

67
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,480
I saw you were distracted
back in the hospital room.

68
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,759
Who were you chatting with?

69
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:40,319
I think I've started

70
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,600
liking someone lately at work.

71
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,319
Liao Bei?

72
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,959
Am I blind?

73
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,399
To get away from him,

74
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:51,319
I got a part-time job at a funeral home.

75
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,079
I met a mortician.

76
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,079
Pretty handsome.

77
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:58,560
How does he treat you? Does he like you?

78
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,759
Of course he does.

79
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:03,279
Otherwise, why would he
always help me move bodies?

80
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,399
See?

81
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:09,480
He gets worried
if I don't reply in two minutes.

82
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,360
He can't be without me.

83
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:15,160
(One Million)
(I gave you one day to visit Mrs. Ji.)

84
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,680
(It's been days. Get back to work.)

85
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:19,120
(I want hangover turtle soup.
Come back to make it.)

86
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:22,319
(If you're not here
in three hours, you're dead.)

87
00:06:24,672 --> 00:06:25,199
What's wrong?

88
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,439
Xuan.

89
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,360
So annoying. Liao Bei insists
on having turtle soup right now.

90
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,639
I have to go.

91
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,399
It's cold outside. Wear my jacket.

92
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,160
What about you?

93
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,120
My home's close.

94
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,439
Liao Bei.

95
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:11,279
I asked you to join me for tea,
not to be a spectator.

96
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,519
My mother-in-law's kidneys are failing.

97
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,040
My medical report shows

98
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:21,279
there's a chance I could be a match.

99
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:26,079
Being the other man,
you're even willing to give up a kidney?

100
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:28,360
You've never loved someone.
You don't understand.

101
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:32,160
If your mother-in-law
and I fell into the water...

102
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,399
Don't embarrass yourself.

103
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,439
Heartless.

104
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,079
Heartbroken.

105
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,360
I'm pretty heartbroken.

106
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,639
Ask your mother-in-law to get actors.

107
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,160
Enough talk.

108
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:44,560
All's ready?

109
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,279
What are you doing?

110
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,879
Tomorrow night? Isn't it?

111
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,000
It is tomorrow night.

112
00:08:00,288 --> 00:08:01,480
(No. 13 Lingchen. Bring 5 million.
Call the police, and I’ll kill her.)

113
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,079
Oh, no.

114
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:04,120
This idiot got the date wrong.

115
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,879
Surrounded by people who can't count.

116
00:08:07,168 --> 00:08:07,776
Hello?

117
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,600
It's tomorrow night!

118
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,160
Why are you improvising?

119
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,480
Mr. Liao, what are you talking about?

120
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,439
We did nothing.
Just rehearsing our lines now.

121
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,759
Song, it's not my men.

122
00:08:21,536 --> 00:08:22,656
(Calling Ji Xuan)

123
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,112
Sorry.

124
00:08:26,592 --> 00:08:29,000
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

125
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,799
Sorry.

126
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,759
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

127
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,879
Sorry.

128
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,919
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

129
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,919
(If you lay a finger on Ji Xuan,)

130
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,080
(you won't live to see tomorrow.)

131
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,840
Song, let me.

132
00:08:58,912 --> 00:09:00,082
(Ji Xuan)

133
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,440
Why didn't you answer my call?

134
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,279
What's wrong?
The signal was bad earlier.

135
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,320
Where are you?

136
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:07,000
I just packed dinner.
Now, on my way back to the hospital.

137
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,480
I just received a photo.

138
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:15,960
Glad you're okay.

139
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,919
What photo?

140
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:18,559
A woman being kidnapped.

141
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,600
No face shown.

142
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,559
Wearing clothes exactly like yours.

143
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,720
It's Wu Shu.

144
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,840
It was cold outside,
so I gave her my coat.

145
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:48,320
Wu Shu!

146
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,679
Wu Shu!

147
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:52,840
Wu Shu!

148
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,039
You scared me.

149
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,639
Are you okay?

150
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,240
Ash.

151
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:21,799
Glad you're safe.

152
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,240
Where's the kidnapper?

153
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,600
He lifted his mask, took one look at me,

154
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,919
then cursed and drove off.

155
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,360
Who is that man?

156
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,879
I'm gonna make him pay.

157
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,679
Fully masked. I couldn't see his face.

158
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:39,080
But his voice sounded familiar.

159
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,879
What's wrong?

160
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,639
Sorry.

161
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,639
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

162
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:51,200
Please try again later.

163
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,440
It was a diversion.

164
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:55,399
After realizing it wasn't Ji Xuan,

165
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:56,960
he turned back.

166
00:11:13,268 --> 00:11:15,060
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

167
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:17,100
♪Flickering neon lights♪

168
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:20,628
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

169
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:23,412
♪Every star is♪

170
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:27,572
♪My heartbeat for you♪

171
00:11:28,884 --> 00:11:30,708
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

172
00:11:30,868 --> 00:11:32,420
♪And land in your arms♪

173
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:36,276
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

174
00:11:36,532 --> 00:11:39,092
♪In the blue sky♪

175
00:11:39,156 --> 00:11:43,284
♪Your smile still lingers♪

176
00:11:44,212 --> 00:11:47,860
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

177
00:11:48,116 --> 00:11:51,780
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

178
00:11:51,988 --> 00:11:54,900
♪Can't find a cure♪

179
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:59,412
♪To love you after we've parted♪

180
00:11:59,604 --> 00:12:03,636
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

181
00:12:03,636 --> 00:12:07,500
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

182
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,300
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

183
00:12:09,396 --> 00:12:14,548
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

184
00:12:15,188 --> 00:12:18,900
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

185
00:12:19,092 --> 00:12:21,844
♪Can't find a cure♪

186
00:12:21,972 --> 00:12:26,612
♪To love you after we've parted♪

187
00:12:26,780 --> 00:12:30,548
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

188
00:12:30,772 --> 00:12:34,356
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

189
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,620
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

190
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:41,620
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
